Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:10.533 --> 00:00:16.333
Open WordPress Dashboard, goto Plugins &gt; Add New

00:00:16.333 --> 00:00:23.566
Type 'Fullscreen Slider' &amp; click Search

00:00:23.566 --> 00:00:30.332
Install and activate this plugin

00:00:30.333 --> 00:00:37.866
Goto Appearance &gt; Fullscreen Slider option

00:00:37.866 --> 00:00:42.466
Select the slider effect: fade or slide

00:00:42.466 --> 00:00:49.432
Click 'Add Slide' to upload and add images for slider

00:00:49.433 --> 00:01:04.433
Upload as many image, we upload 3 images

00:01:04.433 --> 00:01:11.799
Click 'Save' button &amp; preview your website now

00:01:11.800 --> 00:01:27.866
Background will show image slideshow on website

00:01:27.866 --> 00:01:33.766
Lets try another plugin, go back to Dashboard

00:01:33.766 --> 00:01:38.266
At add plugin screen, type 'site background slider'

00:01:38.266 --> 00:01:43.166
Install and activate this plugin

00:01:43.166 --> 00:01:47.666
Now goto Appearance &gt; Background slider

00:01:47.666 --> 00:01:55.032
Select Texture overlay option

00:01:55.033 --> 00:02:01.533
Enter correct path of folder containing slider images

00:02:01.533 --> 00:02:07.866
Save changes and preview website now

00:02:07.866 --> 00:02:24.799
Textured image slider will show on website background

00:02:24.800 --> 00:02:40.666
Go back to Plugin settings to change slider speed

00:02:40.666 --> 00:02:52.666
Now slider image change much faster

00:02:52.666 --> 00:02:58.899
Configure speed setting as per your requirement

